{"tid":1381553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[野狗野豬]大家要自保, 有實用工具","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:24:44.000Z","uid":26967,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a5d7bf57c0cc3872a5be84474d862eb01f6b0b","tid":1381553,"uid":26967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"之前睇東張西望, 多左人餵野豬野狗搞到佢地亂咁走, 住偏遠地區既人記得買定枝傍身保護自己, 漁農處既人有時未必咁快趕到。買或自制記得棍身長ｄ(最好剛身, 木易斷)，一寸長一寸強，個圈或者網最好大Ｄ，整太細有Ｄ野狗野豬太大就唔岩用, 如果D野生物物太兇狠, 記得幾個人一齊用幾支制服佢地拖埋一二面等漁農處黎. 或者有時野豬衝埋黎, 前面既人拎D板擋一擋, 拎棍圈既企後面睇準時機會安全D<br />\n<br />\n記得傷害到瀕危物種係犯法, 記得認清物種同埋用果陣唔好傷到佢地!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/2200575113593/O1CN01i8jQfy1cPdbUO4v8U_!!2200575113593.jpg_320x5000Q50s50.jpg_.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi2%2F2200575113593%2FO1CN01i8jQfy1cPdbUO4v8U_%21%212200575113593.jpg_320x5000Q50s50.jpg_.webp&h=bc5bc70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/4050481392/O1CN01kj3kfH1M9ZrSL636o_!!4050481392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi1%2F4050481392%2FO1CN01kj3kfH1M9ZrSL636o_%21%214050481392.jpg&h=048c9b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38f7091b924dbb2c131135e744edaef7ac8926c1","tid":1381553,"uid":265019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWkyQFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWkyQFJ.png&h=a83a069d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FxpXkJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FxpXkJ.jpg&h=c0950235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b128cfcfb5a08c37f4329a1588a1713b08da1b19","tid":1381553,"uid":7143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:25.000Z","msg":"希望大家記住，去到今天運動連登既角色同優勢係乜<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381475\" data-aut